high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the desk.
Pick up pencil from the desk.
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the dresser.
Place pencil on the dresser.
Turn around and walk to the cabinet to your left.
Pick up pencil from the desk.
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the dresser.
Place pencil on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Collecting pencil from different places and arranging them on a dresser.

high_descs: Turn to reach the desk.
Pick up the pencil from the desk.
Turn around to reach the dresser.
Put the pencil on the dresser.
Turn left and head down the passage on the left and turn left to reach the cabinet.
Pick up the pencil from the cabinet.
Turn left and turn right to head down the passage and head to the dresser on the right.
Put the pencil on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put the two pencils on the dresser.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the desk.
Take the pencil from the desk.
Turn around and go near the dresser.
Put the pencil on the dresser.
Turn around and go near the cabinet.
Take another pencil from the cabinet.
Turn around and go near the dresser.
Put the pencil on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Collect the pencil and placed it on the dresser.
